pitals will be developed,\u201d he claimed.\n\nSaying that the Gandaki Province was working to ensure development to the people at the earliest possible time, he stated that development and good governance were the first priority of the Gandaki Province Government.\n\nThe three-storied building of the FNJ Baglung chapter was constructed at the cost of Rs 10.05 million.","title":"Restoration of monarchy unlikely, Chief Minister says - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/15/149202/","video":[]}
